channel.title: Version 5.27 :: Cap'n Hugo Relearrrn Theme
channel.description: 5.27.0 (2024-04-07) Cap'n Hugo 0.121.0 0.121.0 This release requires a newer Cap'n Hugo version. Change Change If th' theme be configured t' generate warnings or errors dur'n build by sett'n image.errorlevel t' either warning or error 'n yer hugo.toml, it will now also generate output if a link fragment be not found 'n th' target plank.
